These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, soy-milk, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
4 different pets are kept: pony, frog, hedgehog, rabbit
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
5. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | tea | soy-milk | hot-chocolate | iced-tea |
| Pet        | pony | frog   | rabbit | hedgehog    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, mystery, sports, spy
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, colombian, egyptian, pakistani
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the australian is on the left of the egyptian##1
3. the egyptian is in an odd position##4
4. the australian is the person watching satire movies##1
5. the colombian is on the right of the egyptian##1
6. the australian is the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | satire  | mystery  | spy |
| Nationality   | pakistani    | australian | egyptian | colombian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, peas, potato, kale
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, disaster, fantasy, crime
1. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
2. the person eating potato is in an even position##4
3. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person eating peas##3
4. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | kale | potato | peas    | cranberry      |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy        | crime     | family | disaster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, camping, singing, gardening
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, hip-hop, soul, r&b
1. the person who's hobby is camping is between the fan of d&b and the fan of r&b##2
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
3. the fan of soul is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | gardening | baking | camping | singing |
| Music-Genre   | soul       | d&b   | hip-hop    | r&b  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, metal, pop, disco
There are 4 different nationalities: french, nigerian, polish, canadian
1. the fan of pop is on the right of the canadian##1
2. the nigerian is the fan of disco##1
3. the polish is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
4. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
5. the fan of pop is in an odd position##4
6. the french is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | metal  | reggae    | pop   | disco       |
| Nationality   | french | canadian | polish | nigerian |

