3. the person watching adventure movies is in an odd position##4
4. the mexican is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the brazilian is on the left or right of the mexican##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure      | romance | scientific | spy |
| Nationality   | turkish | indian     | mexican  | brazilian  |

