.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, documentary, scientific, disaster
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, skateboard, tram, jet-ski
1. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is the person watching romance movies##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
6. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | disaster | scientific | documentary    |
| Transport     | jet-ski | tram  | airplane     | skateboard |

