.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, musician, electrician, writer
4 different pets are kept: hamster, snake, horse, chinchilla
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the musician##3
2. the writer is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the writer##3
4. the writer is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the social-worker is between the writer and the musician##2
6. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the snake is between the social-worker and the owner of the horse##2
8. the social-worker is on the left or right of the musician##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | musician | social-worker      | writer | electrician |
| Pet   | hamster  | chinchilla | snake    | horse            |

