.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, lemon, radish, kiwi
4 different pets are kept: snake, rat, dog, goldfish
1. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
2. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
3. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the rat and the person eating radish##2
4. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating radish is the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | kiwi | lemon   | pear | radish |
| Pet    | goldfish     | rat | snake     | dog  |

