.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, coffee, iced-tea, sprite
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, trance, punk, country
1. the person drinking mirinda is the fan of country##1
2. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the fan of country is between the fan of gospel and the person drinking iced-tea##2
4. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of country is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee       | iced-tea   | mirinda | sprite |
| Music-Genre   | punk | trance | country        | gospel    |

