.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, lemonade, sprite
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, skateboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is baseball is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up   | sprite   | hot-chocolate      | lemonade      |
| Sport      | ice-hockey | skateboarding | volleyball | baseball |

