.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, broccoli, pomegranate, tomato
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, jazz, gospel, funk
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of gospel is in an even position##4
3. the person eating broccoli is in an even position##4
4. the person eating lettuce is on the far right##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is between the fan of jazz and the fan of gospel##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | tomato | broccoli  | pomegranate  | lettuce |
| Music-Genre   | funk  | gospel | dubstep | jazz   |

