.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, camping, fishing, dancing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, cycling, water-polo, rugby
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's hobby is camping##2
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | dancing | camping         | collecting   | fishing |
| Sport   | water-polo    | cycling | rugby | sailing   |

