.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, rock-climbing, dancing, collecting
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, golf, cycling, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | fishing | dancing    | collecting |
| Sport   | lacrosse   | cycling  | skiing | golf     |

