.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, puzzles, filmmaking, reading
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, pakistani, mexican, thai
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an even position##4
3. the pakistani is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the mexican is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
5. the pakistani is between the thai and the mexican##2
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | reading   | filmmaking | dancing | puzzles    |
| Nationality   | mexican | pakistani  | thai     | argentine |

