.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, almond-milk, lemonade, soy-milk
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, radish, onion, tomato
1. the person eating radish is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
5. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
6. the person eating onion is in an even position##4
7. the person eating pineapple is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | cola    | lemonade       | almond-milk |
| Food       | radish  | onion | tomato | pineapple  |

