.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, british, australian, french
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, car, subway, quad-bike
1. the turkish is on the left of the french##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
4. the person driving the car is on the right of the australian##1
5. the turkish is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
6. the person driving the ship is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | british | australian | turkish  | french |
| Transport     | ship      | subway       | car | quad-bike     |

