.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, social-worker, chef, fisherman
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, skateboard, trike, airplane
1. the social-worker is in an even position##4
2. the social-worker is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
3. the person driving the skateboard is between the nurse and the person driving the bike##2
4. the social-worker is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the trike is on the right of the fisherman##1
6. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | nurse | chef   | fisherman | social-worker |
| Transport   | airplane          | skateboard | bike         | trike  |

 